      "content": "that sounds way too invasive. if the \"central hub\" is just analyzing me to \"adjust preferences,\" why does it feel like it's tracking my schedule too? like, the fridge makes noise right when i'm about to head out or when i'm staying in late. do you think there's a way for these devices to sync up and build a profile of my daily routine without me knowing?",
